sub_title: Business Development Manager - Layco Medical Devices
summary:
I firmly believe that technology has improved our quality of life as many life science innovations are bringing more accessible and effective healthcare to the markets. I want to contribute to this technological revolution and create value for the healthcare of the future by bringing the best technologies to market. 

I consider myself a creative thinker who likes to bring innovative ideas to the table. I believe that I get the best feeling of satisfaction when I share successes with a team. Therefore, I enjoy being part of a proactive team with whom I am able to brainstorm to find optimal solutions. I am a fast learner and I am not afraid to accept big challenges. During my internship, I have learned web development and e-learning tools from scratch. Moreover, I am multilingual; besides my mother tongue (Spanish), I also speak English and Dutch and recently started learning Portuguese.
